---
title: Italian Pesto & Chickpea Stew with Risoni, Toasted Pine Nuts & Parmesan Cheese
description: Here’s how to get all the deep, rich flavours of a risotto with no stirring or extra work! Simply use handy risoni – the little grain-shaped pasta soaks up all the flavour for a simple and tasty side dish. Topped with pesto, chickpeas and sweet roasted veggies, this is comfort food at its finest.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-pesto-chickpea-stew-6c0457ef.jpg
